  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the toor dal and soak it in water for 30 minutes",
    "Drain and boil the toor dal in 2 cups of water until it is soft",
    "Heat ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds, coriander powder, and turmeric powder",
    "Add the cooked toor dal to the pan and stir well",
    "Season with salt to taste",
    "Prepare the pandan leaves by washing and drying them",
    "Spoon the toor dal mixture onto the center of a pandan leaf",
    "Fold the pandan leaf to form a triangle and press gently to shape like nigiri",
    "Repeat with the remaining ingredients"
